<figureCitation box="[210,304,835,861]" captionStart="FIGURE 7" captionStartId="12.[151,250,1936,1960]" captionTargetBox="[205,1376,707,1907]" captionTargetId="figure-204@12.[199,1388,705,1912]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="FIGURE 7. Eccoptolonthus fuyuensis Fei &amp; Zhou, sp. nov. A. Habitus; B. aedeagus, dorsal (parameral side) view; C. aedeagus, lateral view; D. sternite IX of male; E. tergite X of male; F. sternite VIII of male; g. stylus of tergite IX of male. Scale bars, A, B, C, D, E, F, G, H= 0.2 mm;" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4640491" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4640491/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="487">Figs. 7F</figureCitation>
