<figureCitation box="[808,841,871,897]" captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="13.[151,250,1916,1940]" captionTargetBox="[270,1307,181,1878]" captionTargetId="figure-19@13.[265,1323,181,1892]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURE 8. Eccoptolonthus fuyuensis Fei &amp; Zhou, sp. nov. A. aedeagus, dorsal (parameral side) view; B. aedeagus, lateral view; C. sternite IX of male; D. tergite X of male; E. sternite VIII of male; F. stylus of tergite IX of male. Scale bars, A, B= 0.1 mm; C, D= 0.13 mm; E, F= 0.18 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4640495" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4640495/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="487">8F</figureCitation>
